00:00:52.280 --> 00:00:55.020
=Episode 16=

00:01:04.133 --> 00:01:05.990
Young Madam,
I've come to deliver the ledgers.

00:01:12.533 --> 00:01:13.070
Young Madam?

00:01:16.613 --> 00:01:17.732
I brought the ledgers.

00:01:39.290 --> 00:01:39.973
This isn't good.

00:01:47.212 --> 00:01:48.092
What did you see?

00:02:08.092 --> 00:02:08.652
Lan Mengyan!

00:02:40.932 --> 00:02:42.333
He struck first.

00:02:43.293 --> 00:02:44.972
Good thing I was prepared,

00:02:45.773 --> 00:02:46.372
or

00:02:47.493 --> 00:02:48.532
I wouldn't be alive.

00:02:55.293 --> 00:02:56.013
Zhu,

00:02:59.252 --> 00:03:01.293
I've finally avenged you.

00:04:09.573 --> 00:04:10.412
Doesn't it hurt?

00:04:12.493 --> 00:04:13.733
Should it?

00:04:16.973 --> 00:04:18.493
He's yours to deal with now.

00:04:22.070 --> 00:04:23.990
It's time for me
to enter the Jade Spy Bureau.

00:04:26.533 --> 00:04:27.012
All right.

00:04:33.093 --> 00:04:33.853
Wear this.

00:04:35.000 --> 00:04:35.990
It's for your protection.

00:04:37.012 --> 00:04:38.812
They'll likely search you
when you enter,

00:04:39.692 --> 00:04:42.452
so hide it somewhere
they won't check easily.

00:05:03.413 --> 00:05:04.190
Help me put it on.

00:05:44.332 --> 00:05:45.252
I wish you the best.

00:05:56.562 --> 00:05:59.075
(Three days later,
at the Jade Spy Bureau)

00:06:06.413 --> 00:06:08.012
(The prison I once knew,)

00:06:08.692 --> 00:06:10.213
(when did it become so peaceful?)

00:06:15.772 --> 00:06:17.012
Wind and rain may batter it,

00:06:18.332 --> 00:06:19.733
but bamboo never bows.

00:06:20.772 --> 00:06:21.733
A lady's worth

00:06:22.653 --> 00:06:24.012
comes not from her family,

00:06:24.413 --> 00:06:26.613
but from the strength of her character.

00:06:33.132 --> 00:06:33.613
Ma'am.

00:06:37.892 --> 00:06:39.533
You must be Miss Lan.

00:06:42.892 --> 00:06:44.533
(Instructor of the Jade Spy Bureau)
My name is Tong Yan.

00:06:44.892 --> 00:06:46.012
I handle general duties here.

00:06:46.533 --> 00:06:47.853
You may call me by name,

00:06:48.252 --> 00:06:49.853
or address me as Ms. Tong.

00:06:50.733 --> 00:06:51.332
Ms. Tong.

00:06:54.653 --> 00:06:56.572
Ladies trained here

00:06:56.932 --> 00:06:58.252
must master the Six Arts.

00:06:59.173 --> 00:07:00.812
You'll study poetry,
rites, and classics,

00:07:01.012 --> 00:07:02.613
learn riding and archery,

00:07:02.733 --> 00:07:04.733
and understand reason,
discretion, and restraint.

00:07:05.892 --> 00:07:06.892
Only then

00:07:07.372 --> 00:07:09.533
can one be called a lady.

00:07:11.452 --> 00:07:12.733
(Library)
This is the Library.

00:07:13.413 --> 00:07:15.493
Ladies spend much
of their time here reading.

00:07:17.700 --> 00:07:18.293
I hit the mark!

00:07:18.413 --> 00:07:19.093
You did.

00:07:23.093 --> 00:07:25.533
The courtyard holds riding
and archery lessons every morning.

00:07:26.413 --> 00:07:28.692
Women elsewhere in the capital
aren't allowed to train

00:07:29.213 --> 00:07:30.293
in martial skills, but here,

00:07:30.490 --> 00:07:32.590
you may take up bow,
blade, spear, anything you like.

00:07:33.173 --> 00:07:34.493
If you're interested,

00:07:34.853 --> 00:07:36.213
you can give it a try tomorrow.

00:07:37.372 --> 00:07:38.452
A woman in this world

00:07:39.090 --> 00:07:40.572
should follow the example of bamboo.

00:07:40.892 --> 00:07:43.050
That is Master Zhu Lv,

00:07:43.060 --> 00:07:44.490
the director of the Jade Spy Bureau.

00:07:46.653 --> 00:07:47.590
Women are born gentle,

00:07:48.093 --> 00:07:49.493
yet must strive to be strong.

00:07:50.213 --> 00:07:51.252
A true lady doesn't rely

00:07:51.790 --> 00:07:53.213
on deities or fate for protection.

00:07:53.493 --> 00:07:54.853
(The Jade Spy Bureau)

00:07:55.413 --> 00:07:57.493
(isn't the same place it was
when I was last here.)

00:07:58.575 --> 00:08:00.414
(However,
this picture of warmth and harmony)

00:08:00.987 --> 00:08:02.667
(may be more troublesome)

00:08:03.337 --> 00:08:04.378
(than swords and chains.)

00:08:15.692 --> 00:08:16.293
Director,

00:08:16.733 --> 00:08:18.973
this is the new entrant, Miss Lan.

00:08:19.300 --> 00:08:20.530
She's here to pay her respects.

00:08:20.653 --> 00:08:22.132
(Zhu Lv, Director of the Jade Spy Bureau)
Miss Lan, you carry yourself well.

00:08:22.892 --> 00:08:24.252
You must've read a fair bit.

00:08:24.413 --> 00:08:26.213
Have you studied Women's Precepts?

00:08:28.533 --> 00:08:29.372
A little.

00:08:30.733 --> 00:08:31.973
Ban Zhao wrote those teachings

00:08:32.132 --> 00:08:33.733
for palace women,

00:08:34.213 --> 00:08:35.573
yet many misunderstand them,

00:08:35.853 --> 00:08:37.772
thinking they demand blind obedience.

00:08:38.132 --> 00:08:39.252
But here,

00:08:39.573 --> 00:08:41.052
a woman should be like bamboo,

00:08:41.252 --> 00:08:43.412
humble yet unyielding,
aspiring to reach for the sky.

00:08:43.892 --> 00:08:45.772
What do you think?

00:08:48.412 --> 00:08:49.252
Your view is lofty.

00:08:50.093 --> 00:08:51.060
However, this strays far

00:08:51.453 --> 00:08:53.772
from the traditional education
bestowed upon women.

00:08:54.172 --> 00:08:57.052
Can a woman with such principles
survive in this world?

00:08:57.573 --> 00:08:59.652
True gold fears no fire.

00:09:00.213 --> 00:09:01.853
Since you've entered the bureau,

00:09:02.213 --> 00:09:04.252
you'll understand in time.

00:09:10.012 --> 00:09:10.453
Please.

00:09:15.772 --> 00:09:16.973
Peaceful! Peaceful!

00:09:27.125 --> 00:09:28.150
(Charity Chest)

00:09:28.892 --> 00:09:30.213
(What a name for it.)

00:09:31.093 --> 00:09:32.453
(Charity Chest)
(No doubt charity on the surface)

00:09:32.772 --> 00:09:33.813
(and profit in truth.)

00:09:34.052 --> 00:09:35.573
The bureau keeps a charity chest.

00:09:36.132 --> 00:09:37.012
All donations

00:09:37.590 --> 00:09:39.652
go toward sheltering women
who've lost their homes

00:09:39.733 --> 00:09:40.933
or suffered misfortune.

00:09:41.292 --> 00:09:42.372
If you're inclined,

00:09:42.532 --> 00:09:44.613
you may contribute as well.

00:09:46.810 --> 00:09:48.190
Director Zhu, your heart is noble.

00:09:48.252 --> 00:09:49.292
Once I'm settled,

00:09:49.652 --> 00:09:51.453
I'll gladly offer what I can

00:09:51.772 --> 00:09:52.693
for those poor women.

00:09:53.372 --> 00:09:53.813
Good.

00:09:55.493 --> 00:09:56.093
Miss Lan,

00:09:56.733 --> 00:09:59.892
training here requires a small fee.

00:10:05.737 --> 00:10:08.562
(Charity Chest)

00:10:10.587 --> 00:10:16.662
(Charity Chest)

00:10:17.892 --> 00:10:18.412
Ruan.

00:10:19.093 --> 00:10:19.573
Come here.

00:10:32.012 --> 00:10:33.613
Miss Lan, you may call me Ruan.

00:10:35.333 --> 00:10:36.772
You'll be sharing a room from now on,

00:10:37.012 --> 00:10:39.093
so look after each other like sisters.

00:10:39.453 --> 00:10:40.012
Miss Lan,

00:10:40.693 --> 00:10:43.733
treat the Jade Spy Bureau
as your home in the capital from now on.

00:10:47.973 --> 00:10:49.132
Miss Lan, please come with me.

00:10:52.312 --> 00:10:57.350
(Charity Chest)

00:11:00.350 --> 00:11:01.933
This room gets good air from the window.

00:11:02.093 --> 00:11:03.252
If you don't mind,

00:11:03.453 --> 00:11:04.532
stay here for now.

00:11:07.613 --> 00:11:09.213
I'll bring you a fresh set of bedding.

00:11:11.453 --> 00:11:12.213
I'll help.

00:11:21.772 --> 00:11:22.573
Miss Ruan,

00:11:23.333 --> 00:11:24.933
how long have you been here?

00:11:26.372 --> 00:11:27.052
Five years.

00:11:30.052 --> 00:11:31.493
I heard the bureau

00:11:31.652 --> 00:11:32.853
names one woman each year

00:11:33.012 --> 00:11:34.450
as a lady renowned across the world.

00:11:34.933 --> 00:11:37.772
Do you know how many girls are competing

00:11:37.933 --> 00:11:39.132
for that title this year?

00:11:39.892 --> 00:11:40.933
I only ask

00:11:41.172 --> 00:11:42.532
because if there are too many,

00:11:44.532 --> 00:11:46.333
I might as well give up.

00:11:47.350 --> 00:11:49.733
In the five years I've been here,
more than a thousand girls

00:11:49.813 --> 00:11:51.093
have come and gone.

00:11:51.892 --> 00:11:52.733
Only the director

00:11:53.372 --> 00:11:55.172
knows the precise figure,

00:11:55.412 --> 00:11:57.573
as it is recorded in his register.

00:11:58.532 --> 00:11:59.813
All the important registers

00:12:00.012 --> 00:12:03.093
are locked in his cabinet
and watched over by appointed staff.

00:12:07.532 --> 00:12:09.933
No wonder this bureau operates
in such meticulous order.

00:12:10.093 --> 00:12:11.733
The director deserves credit for that.

00:12:12.333 --> 00:12:13.292
I heard

00:12:13.453 --> 00:12:14.933
you came to the bureau

00:12:15.093 --> 00:12:16.213
because of your lover.

00:12:16.693 --> 00:12:18.172
What's your beloved's name?

00:12:21.012 --> 00:12:21.652
Mr. Mo.

00:12:22.532 --> 00:12:23.172
The director

00:12:23.292 --> 00:12:25.132
has trained many distinguished ladies.

00:12:25.333 --> 00:12:26.412
If we study hard,

00:12:26.613 --> 00:12:27.213
your beloved

00:12:27.453 --> 00:12:28.733
will surely come back to you.